.warehouse-reports__other-reports
  %h3 Operational Reports
  .row
    .col-sm-4
      %p
        = link_to warehouse_reports_chronic_index_path do
          Potentially Chronic Clients
        %br
        Disabled clients who are currently homeless and have been in a project at least 12 of the last 36 months. Calculated using HMIS data.
    .col-sm-4
      %p
        = link_to warehouse_reports_first_time_homeless_index_path do
          First Time Homeless
        %br
        Clients who first used residential services within a given date range.
    .col-sm-4
      %p
        = link_to warehouse_reports_open_enrollments_no_service_index_path do
          Open Bed-Night Enrollments with No Recent Service
        %br
        This report is a bit slow to load
      
  %br
  .row
    .col-sm-4
      %p
        = link_to warehouse_reports_client_in_project_during_date_range_index_path do
          Clients in a project for a given date range
        %br
        Who was enrolled at a specific project during a given time.
    .col-sm-4
      %p
        = link_to warehouse_reports_active_veterans_path do
          Active Veterans for a given date range
        %br
        Find veterans who were homeless during a date range, limitable by project type.
    .col-sm-4
      %p
        = link_to warehouse_reports_find_by_id_index_path do
          Bulk Find Client Details by ID
        %br
        Lookup clients by warehouse ID.  Useful for doing research outside of the warehouse and then reconnecting clients.
      
  .row
    
    .col-sm-4
      %p
        = link_to warehouse_reports_veteran_details_exits_path do
          Veteran Exits
        %br
        Details of veterans who exited from homelessness during a given date range.
    .col-sm-4
      %p
        = link_to warehouse_reports_disabilities_path do
          Enrolled clients with selected disabilities
        %br
        Find currently enrolled clients based on disabilities
    .col-sm-4
      %p
        = link_to warehouse_reports_chronic_housed_index_path do
          Clients Housed, Previously on the Chronic List
        %br
        See who was housed in permanent housing after being on the chronic list. 

  %br
  .row
    .col-sm-4
      %p
        = link_to "HUD Chronic", warehouse_reports_hud_chronics_path
        %br
        Clients who meet the HUD definition of Chronically Homeless as outlined in the 
        = link_to 'HMIS Glossary.', 'https://www.hudexchange.info/resource/4489/hmis-standard-reporting-terminology-glossary/'
        Calculated using self-report data from entry assessments.
      

